{"tid":2076109,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"Live：中国在港舉行諮詢 收集公眾對国安法意見","createTime":"2020-06-23T09:37:51.000Z","updateTime":"2020-06-23T09:38:45.000Z","uid":7542,"like":1,"dislike":5,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"8e1537494f5198b5e6b3ac596f8c25edc66be39a","tid":2076109,"uid":7542,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-23T09:37:51.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">唔該，你睇清楚<strong><ins>公眾</ins></strong>即係咩人：</span><br />\n<br />\n- 前律政司司長<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">袁國強</span></strong> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n- 身兼基本法委員會委員的港大<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">法律學者陳弘毅</span></strong><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n- 本身是資深大律師的<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">監警會主席</strong><strong>梁定邦</span></strong><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n- 行政會議成員任志剛<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/z.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n- 前行會成員梁智鴻<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/z.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">題外話：當年喺港大法學院見到陳弘毅對中國 visitor 嗰種恭維嘅方法，真係諗起都想嘔</span></strong><br />\n<br />\n《人民日報》報道，有中央官員今日在香港主持多場座談會，向香港各界人士繼續廣泛收集「港區國安法」的意見與建議。行政會議成員任志剛、身兼基本法委員會委員的港大法律學者陳弘毅、本身是資深大律師的監警會主席梁定邦，以及前行會成員梁智鴻等，下午陸續到中聯辦，預料是出席座談會。據了解，前律政司司長袁國強亦有出席。《人民日報》報道指，「港區國安法」備受關注，中央注重收集香港社會各界意見，密集透過各種形式聽取民意。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1533657-20200623.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1533657-20200623.htm&d=91nyg34XrGq4aGOua7i4JaS5T01Y9%2BWuDWMC0%2BQyx7Y%3D&h=52af6a29\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1533657-20200623.htm&h=3ca92005\" target=\"_blank\">https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1533657-20200623.htm</a>"},{"pid":"303140e0d3043f032504d60fe753537cffcb5863","tid":2076109,"uid":7542,"like":0,"dislike":